assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Asahi Kogyosha Co., Ltd. primarily engages in the air-conditioning and sanitation installation works in Japan. It also designs and develops precision environmental control equipment for industries involved in manufacturing semiconductors and liquid crystal panels. Asahi Kogyosha Co., Ltd. was founded in 1925 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
